   {
      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "All newly-created wallets will be HD, though, and supporting a matrix of HD, Segwit, Watch-Only, etc, etc and all combinations thereof blows up maintinence complexity a ton. In any case, a watch-only wallet is going to need a mode that forces it to never generate new addresses, so having an HD seed or not having an HD seed wont matter - you still wont get new addresses.",
      "created_at" : "2017-10-30T23:22:26Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/11582#issuecomment-340614129",
