   {
      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Since #9662 should be disabling all forms of key generation, I don't see why you need to have `-usehd=0`. Why can't you just have a wallet type which has no private keys whatsoever? Instead of doing `-usehd=0`, you just have `-disablehot` which then doesn't generate a HD master key or any other key.",
