   {
      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "@TheBlueMatt Watchonly-only wallets aren't HD. Maintenance complexity isn't affected, because we still need to support non-HD wallets regardless. I see no value in writing an ignored HD seed - it only creates the risk that we accidentally use it rather than crash or fail.\r\n\r\n@achow101 I suppose that's a possibility, but I don't see the harm in having the option...",
